<doc id="1117728" wikidata="Q16834750" url="?curid=1117728" title="Association Control Service Element">
<text>Association Control Service Element (ACSE) is the OSI method for establishing a call between one application programs. ACSE checks the identities and contexts of the application entities, and could apply an authentication security check.

